<lb/><opener><dateline rend="right"><placeName><settlement type="town">Hamilton</settlement></placeName> <add place="above" hand="#U">25 <seg rend="right">62</seg></add> <date when="1865-08-08">8 August
<lb/>18<add place="inline">[64]</add></date></dateline>
<lb/>
<lb/><salute>My Dear <persName>M<hi rend="sup underline">rs</hi> Noel</persName></salute></opener>
<lb/><p>The kind true
<lb/>heartedness of your
<lb/>father and mother-
<lb/>at <placeName><unclear cert="medium">Marley House</unclear></placeName>
<lb/>I can never forget
<lb/>and I thank you 
<lb/>for your very
<lb/>kind invitation
<lb/>and evident
<lb/>desire to follow

	<pb facs="liv_002043_0002" n="0002"/>
<lb/>in your dear parents
<lb/>"<unclear cert="low">spoon</unclear>" but I am <!--added quotes-->
<lb/>very anxious to get
<lb/>back to Africa again
<lb/>and endeavour to
<lb/>open up the country
<lb/>South of the Portuguese
<lb/>so that my past
<lb/>labours may not
<lb/>be rendered <hi rend="underline">further<!--fruitless--></hi>
<lb/>by these inveterate
<lb/>slavers - I left my
<lb/>steamer at <placeName><settlement type="city"><unclear cert="medium">Bombay</unclear></settlement></placeName>
<lb/>for this very purpose
<lb/>and am now only
<lb/>anxious to get <unclear cert="medium">out of</unclear>
<lb/>a <unclear cert="medium">retired</unclear> nook to do

	<pb facs="liv_002043_0003" n="0003"/>
<lb/>a little work and then
<lb/>be off. my daughter <!--person?-->
<lb/>now woman grown
<lb/>is to keep my cottage
<lb/>as I wish to be near
<lb/>her as much as
<lb/>possible - I avoid
<lb/>all public engagement
<lb/>except Bath - I
<lb/>mention these
<lb/>things that you
<lb/>may see that I do 
<lb/>not undervalue
<lb/>your generous
<lb/>hospitality though
<lb/>I have to decline it

	<pb facs="liv_002043_0004" n="0004"/>
<lb/>I beg you to present
<lb/>my kind salutation 
<lb/>to your husband &amp;
<lb/>accept my warmest
<lb/>thanks for your
<lb/>kind offer
</p>

